"bbox": [202.9, 680.9, 535.4, 693.0]}, {"text": "Major Bleeding 4 (6%) 0 (0%) 0.022*", "bbox": [202.9, 695.2, 539.8, 708.7]}, {"text": "  In-Hospital Transfusion 4 (6%) 1 (1%) 0.074", "bbox": [202.9, 710.6, 535.4, 722.7]}, {"text": "LVT* 0 (0%) 0 (0%) —", "bbox": [202.9, 724.9, 524.4, 738.4]}, {"text": "Table 2. In-Hospital Clinical Events. MACCE: Major adverse cardiovascular and cerebrovascular event. TLR:", "bbox": [198.9, 748.3, 698.4, 764.2]}, {"text": "Target lesion revascularization. LVT: Left ventricular thrombus. *LVT was an exclusion criterion for this", "bbox": [198.9, 760.7, 673.5, 778.1]}, {"text": "analysis.", "bbox": [198.9, 774.2, 237.5, 789.8]}, {"text": "Clinical follow-up at 4 months was available in 97% of patients. The rate of the primary NACE composite", "bbox": [214.3, 826.5, 708.9, 842.0]}, {"text": "outcome was 27% with the selective TATT strategy (CHUM) compared to 19% with the ticagrelor-DAPT strategy", "bbox": [198.9, 839.3, 708.8, 854.8]}, {"text": "(CHUS; p = 0.342). Comparison of MACCE alone (21% vs 19%, p = 0.844) was also non-significant, but there", "bbox": [198.9, 852.0, 709.0, 867.6]}, {"text": "was a significant excess of major bleeding with the selective TATT strategy (7% vs 0%, p = 0.019) and a trend in", "bbox": [198.9, 864.8, 708.9, 880.3]}, {"text": "terms of an increase in the irreversible events composite outcome (15% vs 6%, p = 0.104; Table 4). The results", "bbox": [198.9, 877.6, 708.9, 893.1]}, {"text": "of subgroup analyses based on LVEF and the extent of apical dysfunction are shown in Supplementary Material", "bbox": [198.9, 890.2, 709.0, 905.9]}, {"text": "(Table A1). After multivariate regression with instrumental variable analysis, admission hemoglobin predicted", "bbox": [198.9, 903.2, 708.7, 918.7]}, {"text": "NACE, major bleeding, and treatment failure, whereas the presence of cardiogenic shock was an independent", "bbox": [198.9, 915.9, 708.9, 931.5]}, {"text": "SCientifiC REPORTS | (2018) 8:10326 | DOI:10.1038/s41598-018-28676-4 3", "bbox": [52.1, 964.7, 708.9, 979.9]}]}